FBIS4-61445 "drsov088_f_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-088 Daily Report 5 May 1994 National Affairs No Bomb Found No Bomb Found LD0505192594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1831 GMT 5 May 94 LD0505192594 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Report by UKRINFORM correspondent Lev Ryabchikov for TASS] [Text] Simferopol 5 May TASS--No mine has been found in the building of the Crimean local government. By 0200 on Thursday [5 May] afternoon, field engineers of the Black Sea Fleet's 126th Coastal Guard Division completed inspection of the building but failed to detect the reported explosive device. The inspection was prompted by a telephone call this morning. An unidentified person said a mine had been planted in the government building, after which a government session was broken off and everybody was evacuated from the building.
